9 10:01 UTC\\n\\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1775728883395,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"9abbcf08\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [],\n          \"stopReason\": \"error\",\n          \"api\": \"ollama\",\n          \"provider\": \"ollama\",\n          \"model\": \"qwen3:8b\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 0,\n            \"output\": 0,\n            \"totalTokens\": 0,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"timestamp\": 1775729002845,\n          \"errorMessage\": \"This operation was aborted\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"1774965c\",\n            \"seq\": 2\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:prometeo:whatsapp:group:120363407571517396@g.us\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n      \"displayName\": \"whatsapp:g-tradelab\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"to\": \"120363407571517396@g.us\",\n        \"accountId\": \"default\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776129084872,\n      \"sessionId\": \"f2be9ee6-81d0-4c08-93e2-e92fb7209198\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 272000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 104975,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 4.193683999999999,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776129067814,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776129084860,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 17046,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"whatsapp\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"120363407571517396@g.us\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"default\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\prometeo\\\\sessions\\\\f2be9ee6-81d0-4c08-93e2-e92fb7209198.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \" Claro. Te dejo **uno bueno, directo y usable** para promocionar TradeLab:\\n\\n`Create a premium Instagram ad for TradeLab, a trading journal app for serious traders. Show a sleek dark-mode app interface with modules for trade journaling, discipline score, progress tracking, and setup review. The composition should feel clean, modern, high-performance, and trustworthy. Use a premium fintech aesthetic with deep navy tones, blue and emerald highlights, subtle glow, and cinematic lighting. The image should communicate discipline, clarity, and trader improvement. Minimal clutter, elegant product-focused layout, highly polished SaaS advertisement style, Instagram 4:5.`\\n\\nSi quieres, te doy ahora mismo **3 versiones de ese mismo prompt**:\\n- más premium\\n- más emocional\\n- más agresiva para conversión.\",\n              \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0dbcdf7ab4acaa500169dd93aaecf481919c4b3dc69fd8f274\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 349,\n            \"output\": 171,\n            \"totalTokens\": 103432,\n            \"cacheRead\": 102912,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.029165499999999997\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776128933627,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_0dbcdf7ab4acaa500169dd93a97eb88191b5042b6ce18ae708\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"40bfd38e\",\n            \"seq\": 244\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"[media attached: C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\media\\\\inbound\\\\fc1f7d71-6b55-4975-8b78-575e588c2c0a.jpg (image/jpeg)]\\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\\n\\n\\n<media:image>\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"image\",\n              \"mimeType\": \"image/jpeg\",\n              \"omitted\": true,\n              \"bytes\": 135788\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776129067813,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"cdeb8931\",\n            \"seq\": 245\n          },\n          \"senderLabel\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \" Va por buen camino, pero **todavía se ve muy genérica/AI ad**.\\n\\n**Lo bueno**\\n- se entiende rápido que es una app para traders\\n- el teléfono como héroe funciona\\n- la estética dark/premium sí va con TradeLab\\n\\n**Lo flojo**\\n- el copy arriba y abajo está demasiado genérico\\n- “the only journal for serious traders” suena inflado\\n- la UI del teléfono no se siente 100% TradeLab real\\n- se ve más como ad de app cualquiera que como marca con identidad propia\\n- demasiado “stock + mockup AI”\\n\\n**Qué mejoraría**\\n1. **menos texto**\\n   - deja una sola frase fuerte\\n   - no headline arriba + slogan abajo peleando\\n\\n2. **copy más propio**\\n   - mejor algo como:\\n     - **Stop trading on memory and emotion**\\n     - **Journal your trades. Sharpen your discipline.**\\n     - **Review better. Trade cleaner.**\\n\\n3. **más foco en producto**\\n   - acercar más la UI\\n   - menos fondo tipo stock trader\\n\\n4. **hacerla más TradeLab**\\n   - usar nombres/módulos más parecidos al producto real\\n   - discipline score más cercano al de la app\\n   - menos texto random dentro del phone\\n\\n5. **menos “serious trader cliché”**\\n   - ahora cae un poco en eso\\n   - mejor mostrar claridad y control, no solo pose\\n\\n**Mi recomendación**\\nSi haces otra versión, yo la orientaría a:\\n- menos copy\\n- más app\\n- menos persona al fondo\\n- más identidad visual propia\\n\\n**Prompt corregido**\\n`Create a premium Instagram ad for TradeLab with the phone screen as the main focus. Show a sleek dark-mode trading journal interface inspired by a real fintech product, with modules for trade journal, discipline score, progress review, and setup analysis. Keep the background minimal and cinematic, with only subtle hints of a trader workspace. Avoid stock-photo vibes and avoid generic motivational ad style. The image should feel clean, modern, sharp, and product-led. Use deep navy, blue, and emerald accents. Add only one short headline: \\\"Stop trading on memory and emotion\\\". Instagram 4:5.`\\n\\nSi quieres, te saco **3 prompts mejores** basados en esta imagen:\\n- una más product-led\\n- una más premium\\n- una más agresiva para conversión.\",\n              \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0dbcdf7ab4acaa500169dd9432aa6081918705bc260975b03e\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 104975,\n            \"output\": 506,\n            \"totalTokens\": 105481,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.27002750000000003\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776129067817,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_0dbcdf7ab4acaa500169dd942fb34c8191962ac1c0cd3f2856\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"6447844b\",\n            \"seq\": 246\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:66f48e60-573d-47b9-94f9-40d29cb19542\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: Atlas OS follow-up pulse\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: Atlas OS follow-up pulse\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"to\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776128905190,\n      \"sessionId\": \"a69fc7f9-b261-4700-8213-7baa4faf600e\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 272000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 63052,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 1.4116735000000002,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776128723350,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776128905175,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 12447,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastTo\": \"heartbeat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\main\\\\sessions\\\\a69fc7f9-b261-4700-8213-7baa4faf600e.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"**Evaluating cron summary needs**\\n\\nI’m considering whether I have enough information to provide a plain text summary for cron. I need to infer if the message is truly necessary. To be thorough, I might want to inspect the full datasource log to determine if that would give me the insights required or if the process log is sufficient. It seems a bit unclear right now, so I want to make sure I'm covering all my bases!\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_TJ56Qa