tRun":false,"lastChannel":"whatsapp","lastTo":"120363424964463765@g.us","lastAccountId":"default","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\ares\\sessions\\7378462a-0fe4-43a2-b024-a9e55e23b872.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:c0842f5f-cc85-4724-ac78-4867057e7300 Recordatorio Smart Project pierna mañana 4:40am] Envía al grupo Smart Project un saludo corto, humano y activador porque en 20 minutos, a las 5:00 am, toca cumplir la sesión de pierna que habían movido para hoy. Solo responde con el mensaje final para el grupo; no incluyas logs, reportes internos, confirmaciones técnicas ni metadata.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 9th, 2026 — 5:01 AM (America/Bogota) / 2026-04-09 10:01 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775728883395,"__openclaw":{"id":"9abbcf08","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"stopReason":"error","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"qwen3:8b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"timestamp":1775729002845,"errorMessage":"This operation was aborted","__openclaw":{"id":"1774965c","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:prometeo:whatsapp:group:120363407571517396@g.us","kind":"group","channel":"whatsapp","displayName":"whatsapp:g-tradelab","deliveryContext":{"channel":"whatsapp","to":"120363407571517396@g.us","accountId":"default"},"updatedAt":1776129084872,"sessionId":"f2be9ee6-81d0-4c08-93e2-e92fb7209198","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":104975,"estimatedCostUsd":4.193683999999999,"status":"done","startedAt":1776129067814,"endedAt":1776129084860,"runtimeMs":17046,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"whatsapp","lastTo":"120363407571517396@g.us","lastAccountId":"default","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\prometeo\\sessions\\f2be9ee6-81d0-4c08-93e2-e92fb7209198.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":" Claro. Te dejo **uno bueno, directo y usable** para promocionar TradeLab:\n\n`Create a premium Instagram ad for TradeLab, a trading journal app for serious traders. Show a sleek dark-mode app interface with modules for trade journaling, discipline score, progress tracking, and setup review. The composition should feel clean, modern, high-performance, and trustworthy. Use a premium fintech aesthetic with deep navy tones, blue and emerald highlights, subtle glow, and cinematic lighting. The image should communicate discipline, clarity, and trader improvement. Minimal clutter, elegant product-focused layout, highly polished SaaS advertisement style, Instagram 4:5.`\n\nSi quieres, te doy ahora mismo **3 versiones de ese mismo prompt**:\n- más premium\n- más emocional\n- más agresiva para conversión.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0dbcdf7ab4acaa500169dd93aaecf481919c4b3dc69fd8f274\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":349,"output":171,"totalTokens":103432,"cacheRead":102912,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.029165499999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776128933627,"responseId":"resp_0dbcdf7ab4acaa500169dd93a97eb88191b5042b6ce18ae708","__openclaw":{"id":"40bfd38e","seq":244}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\fc1f7d71-6b55-4975-8b78-575e588c2c0a.jpg (image/jpeg)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\n\n\n<media:image>"},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","omitted":true,"bytes":135788}],"timestamp":1776129067813,"__openclaw":{"id":"cdeb8931","seq":245},"senderLabel":"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)"},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":" Va por buen camino, pero **todavía se ve muy genérica/AI ad**.\n\n**Lo bueno**\n- se entiende rápido que es una app para traders\n- el teléfono como héroe funciona\n- la estética dark/premium sí va con TradeLab\n\n**Lo flojo**\n- el copy arriba y abajo está demasiado genérico\n- “the only journal for serious traders” suena inflado\n- la UI del teléfono no se siente 100% TradeLab real\n- se ve más como ad de app cualquiera que como marca con identidad propia\n- demasiado “stock + mockup AI”\n\n**Qué mejoraría**\n1. **menos texto**\n   - deja una sola frase fuerte\n   - no headline arriba + slogan abajo peleando\n\n2. **copy más propio**\n   - mejor algo como:\n     - **Stop trading on memory and emotion**\n     - **Journal your trades. Sharpen your discipline.**\n     - **Review better. Trade cleaner.**\n\n3. **más foco en producto**\n   - acercar más la UI\n   - menos fondo tipo stock trader\n\n4. **hacerla más TradeLab**\n   - usar nombres/módulos más parecidos al producto real\n   - discipline score más cercano al de la app\n   - menos texto random dentro del phone\n\n5. **menos “serious trader cliché”**\n   - ahora cae un poco en eso\n   - mejor mostrar claridad y control, no solo pose\n\n**Mi recomendación**\nSi haces otra versión, yo la orientaría a:\n- menos copy\n- más app\n- menos persona al fondo\n- más identidad visual propia\n\n**Prompt corregido**\n`Create a premium Instagram ad for TradeLab with the phone screen as the main focus. Show a sleek dark-mode trading journal interface inspired by a real fintech product, with modules for trade journal, discipline score, progress review, and setup analysis. Keep the background minimal and cinematic, with only subtle hints of a trader workspace. Avoid stock-photo vibes and avoid generic motivational ad style. The image should feel clean, modern, sharp, and product-led. Use deep navy, blue, and emerald accents. Add only one short headline: \"Stop trading on memory and emotion\". Instagram 4:5.`\n\nSi quieres, te saco **3 prompts mejores** basados en esta imagen:\n- una más product-led\n- una más premium\n- una más agresiva para conversión.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0dbcdf7ab4acaa500169dd9432aa6081918705bc260975b03e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":104975,"output":506,"totalTokens":105481,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.27002750000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776129067817,"responseId":"resp_0dbcdf7ab4acaa500169dd942fb34c8191962ac1c0cd3f2856","__openclaw":{"id":"6447844b","seq":246}}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:66f48e60-573d-47b9-94f9-40d29cb19542","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Atlas OS follow-up pulse","displayName":"Cron: Atlas OS follow-up pulse","deliveryContext":{"to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1776128905190,"sessionId":"a69fc7f9-b261-4700-8213-7baa4faf600e","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":63052,"estimatedCostUsd":1.4116735000000002,"status":"running","startedAt":1776128723350,"endedAt":1776128905175,"runtimeMs":12447,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\a69fc7f9-b261-4700-8213-7baa4faf600e.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating cron summary needs**\n\nI’m considering whether I have enough information to provide a plain text summary for cron. I need to infer if the message is truly necessary. To be thorough, I might want to inspect the full datasource log to determine if that would give me the insights required or if the process log is sufficient. It seems a bit unclear right now, so I want to make sure I'm covering all my bases!"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_TJ56QaXHk